  "title": "Delivery Driver #77056",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Wholesales</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Delivery Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pandan Loop</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon – Fri, 6.00am – 2.00pm; Sat, 6.00am – 12.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $3,000 + Variable bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Load and unload fruits from/into refrigerated (reefer) containers.</li><li>Unstuff containers as required, ensuring proper handling of produce.</li><li>Sort and pack fruits as needed before delivery.</li><li>Conduct delivery trips to assigned locations in a safe and timely manner.</li><li>Check and verify delivery orders and goods during loading and unloading.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and basic upkeep of assigned vehicle.</li><li>Follow all safety and operational procedures.</li><li>Perform any other related duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Possess a valid Class 3/4 driving license.</li><li>Experience in driving and handling goods, especially perishable items, is an advantage.</li><li>Responsible, punctual, and able to work independently.</li><li>Good communication and teamwork skills.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77056 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
